						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1512 (1590 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Records an endowment of money by <hi rend="bold">Chennarāja,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Tirumalaiyyan of Pattikkoṇḍai,</hi> for offerings during the festival every month for Paramapadanātha. The details of date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1512, Vikṛiti, Ṛishabha, śu. 7, Thursday Pushya correspond to 1590 A.D., April 30, Thursday, ·88; ·10.</hi> </p>						

